OSECP is a open source Game Control Panel for Space Engineers.

This project is a fork of SESM 2.3.1. The latest version of SESM is now under a new EULA and no longer under a BSD open source license.

We are aiming to add new features and maintain compatibility with Server 2012 and Sql Server 2014.
